<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Carbon Footprint Calculator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/carbon.css" />
    <link
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header") %>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
        ‚ôªÔ∏è Carbon Footprint Calculator
      </h1>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h2>üåçEvery Action Leaves a Marküå±</h2>
        <p>
          From the energy we use to the way we travel, every choice impacts our
          planet. A lower footprint means a cleaner Earth‚Äîsmall changes like
          saving electricity, reducing waste, and choosing sustainability can
          create a greener future. Your actions matter‚Äîlet‚Äôs make them count!‚ôªÔ∏è
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="calculator-card animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
        <div class="input-group">
          <label for="waste-type">Select Waste Type</label>
          <select id="waste-type">
            <option value="">Choose a waste type...</option>
            <option value="paper">Paper</option>
            <option value="wood">Wood</option>
            <option value="plastic">Plastic</option>
            <option value="fabric">Fabric</option>
            <option value="food">Food Waste</option>
            <option value="expired">Expired Food</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group">
          <label for="weight">Weight (kg)</label>
          <input
            type="number"
            id="weight"
            min="0"
            step="0.1"
            placeholder="Enter weight in kilograms"
          />
        </div>

        <button onclick="calculateCarbon()">Calculate Carbon Footprint</button>

        <div id="result" class="result-card mb-4">
          <h3 style="color: black">Carbon Footprint Results</h3>
          <p id="carbon-value"></p>
          <p id="comparison"></p>
        </div>

        <div class="waste-list" id="waste-list"></div>

        <div class="eco-tip">
          <h4>üå± Eco Tip of the Day</h4>
          <p id="eco-tip"></p>
        </div>

        <canvas id="emissions-chart"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>   
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/3.7.0/chart.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/carbon.js"></script>

   
  </body>
</html>
